The tv in the bedroom was situated high in the corner of the bedroom on the type of platform you would find in a hospital room.	The suite was large, although with a slightly awkward layout, and the ensuite had a large spa bath with a large hatch through to the bedroom so that someone in the bath could watch the bedroom TV or converse with their partner in the bedroom.	The bed was comfortable, room was equipped with a flat screen TV, and wifi is provided.	The living room was narrow and the TV armoire crowded the room from one side and the oversized 1990's type couch from the other.